# --- figures ---
# Figures ARE tracked: the report and deck embed them, so a reviewer must see
# them in a fresh clone (the submission is judged "reproducible from the
# repository alone"). Regenerate any time with `python -m src.build_all`.
# (data/processed/ above stays ignored — it is large and fully regenerable.)

